Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
This runs the simulation. 
The mode adds RIF contribution to the OD, so this needs to be compared with \
uncorrected data (in the above, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]dataRIFnewMUT12=dataprev\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
ensures this is the case)\
\>", "Subsection",
